A recap on our Soft Opening @eileen.entertainment ! Thank you to everyone who came ! So proud of our partner @saveileen for bringing her vision to life and all that she has accomplished so far ❤️! To many more big things to come! 🔥
.
🎥: @enerizemedia @3mnick 
.
. We will be open from 9-6pm daily ! Come get your custom floral bouquet or even just a coffee 💖☕️💐
.
. address : 5695 E. Charleston Blvd, Suite 139, Las Vegas, NV 89142
.
#lasvegas #floraldesign #floral
